org.gradoop.common.storage.impl.hbase.api

Interface GraphHeadHandler<G extends EPGMGraphHead>

  • Type Parameters:
    G - EPGM graph head type
    All Superinterfaces:
    ElementHandler, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseGraphHeadHandler

    public interface GraphHeadHandler<G extends EPGMGraphHead>
extends ElementHandler
    This class is responsible for reading and writing EPGM graph heads from and to HBase.
